\pard\f0\fs28 The cultivated plant, with tuberous roots, is var.{\i  sisarum} and is of unknown origin. The wild plant is var.{\i  lancifolium} (Bieb.) Thell. ({\i S. lancifolium} Bieb., non Schrank, {\i S. sisaroideum} DC.).
